<title>회원정보 수정</title>
</head>
<body>
	<p id=sect>커뮤니티 가입을 축하합니다.</p>
	<div align="center">
		<HR>
		<form
			action="http://localhost:8787/JSP_BOARD/MemberServlet?cmd=update"
